The Haradrim encampment of D没m Boha is located on the western slopes of the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should collect phials of poison from Haradrim archers.
The Haradrim encampment of D没m Boha is located on the western slopes of the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should collect phials of poison from Haradrim archers.
The Haradrim archers carry a poison with which they coat their arrowheads. Perhaps the Rangers of Ithilien could use such a poison for themselves.

'This Haradrim poison is quite potent. It and its effects are not unknown to the Rangers, nor have we refrained from using it on our own arrows against the Enemy's servants. What you have brought me today will not go to waste, I assure you.'
You should return to Gladhir, who can be found at Haerondir.
